io.spine.query

Class RecordQuery<I,R extends com.google.protobuf.Message>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.query.RecordQuery<I,R>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type of the record identifiers
    R - the type of the stored records
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Query<I,R>

    @SPI
public final class RecordQuery<I,R extends com.google.protobuf.Message>
extends java.lang.Object
    A query for the records each being a stored Protobuf message.

    If the queried Protobuf message defines the state of an entity, EntityQuery serves querying better than this type. See the package-info.java of this package for more details.

    See Also:
    EntityQuery

        public final @Nullable java.lang.Integer limit()
